        public long updateProperties(long propTupleId,

        Updates data of an existing properties tuple by specifying its current property tuple id from a specified Property[] instance which contains new values of properties for a graph element.
        Parameters:
        propTupleId - properties tuple id
        properties - an array containing all properties to be updated for a graph element
        Returns:
